# Database migrations

- Read **`backend/migrations/README.md`** before changing or applying migrations.
- Never run destructive SQL (`DROP DATABASE`, mass `DELETE` without `WHERE`, etc.) unless the user explicitly requests it and understands impact.
- Prefer idempotent patterns (`IF NOT EXISTS`) consistent with existing migration style.
- After applying migrations, use the verification queries documented in the migration README when applicable.
